nodes.text: Jaen Kett was a Human male doctor residing in the planet of Ord Mantell during its Civil War. He was stationed in a hot zone in the island of Mannett Point, where he kept several war orphan kids, protecting them from the conflict. He enlisted the help of a promising sergeant of the Republic and a smuggler to help him get the children to a safer zone. They both accepted to help him, and the children were retrieved to a safer zone in Republic territory.
